              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Reaction products were observed by a pair of",
                "telescopes consisting of 150 mu-m-thick dE and",
                "2000 mu-m-thick E Si surface barrier detectors.",
                "One telescope was fixed at 19.5 degr. for monitoring",
                "purposes, while the other was rotated around the",
                "target and measured the reaction products at lab.",
                "angles between 6.5  and 45 degr."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Experimental error. To keep data acquisition",
                "dead time negligible even for the smallest angles, a",
                "prescaler was used to reduce the number of elastic",
                "scatterg events recorded. This and several other",
                "procedures enable the absolute cross section to be",
                "determined with a precision of +-3.5%."
              ]
            }
